"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"lmplot() is a figure-level function that combines regplot() and FacetGrid. It should not be used with FacetGrid.map(). Instead, use regplot() with FacetGrid.map() or use lmplot() directly.\",\n  \"patch\": \"5,6c5\\n< g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> sns.lmplot(data=tips, x='total_bill', y='tip', col='time', row='sex')\"\n}"